  "body": "The `refund_counter` variable has been defined as U256 in all the forks. However, staring Istanbul, the EVM allows the counter to be negative on a per-frame basis. See #503 for details.\r\n\r\nThe type will have to therefore be changed to `int` instead of `U256`. See [implement EIP-2200](https://github.com/ethereum/execution-specs/pull/503/commits/bc36baaf27da3780d19bc2cf5154eb0bd2dd2a46) for more details.\r\n\r\n",
